            <td valign="top"><span class="style12"><span class="style16">Reference Sites: </span></span></td>
            <td valign="top"><p> <span class="style20">Cincinnati: <a href="http://www.cincinnati-oh.gov/"><font color="#000066">http://www.cincinnati-oh.gov</font></a></span></p>
              <p class="style20"> Charleston, SC: <a href="http://www.ci.charleston.sc.us"><font color="#000066">http://www.ci.charleston.sc.us</font></a> </p>
              <p class="style20"> Salt Lake City: <a href="http://www.ci.slc.ut.us/"><font color="#000066">http://www.ci.slc.ut.us/</font></a></p>
              <p class="style20"> San Diego: <a href="http://www.sandiego.gov/"><font color="#000066">http://www.sandiego.gov/</font></a></p>
            <p class="style20"> Santa Clara County:  <a href="http://www.sccgov.org"><font color="#000066">http://www.sccgov.org</font></a></p></td>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
